</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He&apos;s first referred to as the nickname &quot;Blondie&quot; (Scarr&apos;s name for him), then the nickname &quot;Freitag&quot; (Elsa&apos;s name for him), before we find out his rea<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He's first referred to as the nickname "Blondie" (Scarr's name for him), then the nickname "Freitag" (Elsa's name for him), before we find out his real name. And yes, he's the dogsbody as well. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
