      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1176737-call-for-the-dead">Quotes from Call for the Dead</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Everything he admired or loved had been the product of intense individualism. ...when had mass philosophies ever brought benefit or wisdom?&rdquo;</span>
